"{\"uid\": \"fullfact.org-online-usa-today-fake-report-church-of-satan-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our fact checking systematically raises standards in public debate and changes the behaviour of powerful actors  We are campaigning to tackle bad information online, protect our elections and improve the quality of information in public debate  Our policy work aims to improve the information environment, in order to protect and encourage good public debate  Bad information ruins lives.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 388, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are a team of independent fact checkers and campaigners who find, expose and counter the harm it does  What was claimed  USA Today reported that the Church of Satan praised the Paris Olympics opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 513, \"end\": 522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.799124336460434e-15, \"text\": \"USA Today\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our verdict  False.\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not a genuine news report, and no such comments were made by the Church of Satan.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Avideopurporting to be a USA Today report claims the Church of Satan has thanked the organisers of the opening ceremony for the Paris 2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 739, \"end\": 748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.799124336460434e-15, \"text\": \"USA Today\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this is not a real USA Today report, and the Church of Satan has made no such comment.\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 958, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 891, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.799124336460434e-15, \"text\": \"USA Today\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The clip features a voiceover that says: \\\"The Church of Satan thanked the organisers of the Olympic Games for the magnificent opening ceremony\\\" and supposedly quotes a high priest of the church,Peter H. Gilmore, saying it was a celebration of \\\"freedom from an entrenching divinity\\\".\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1154, \"end\": 1159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Peter\", \"score\": 0.9823208340557339, \"rank\": 0.011710511016273645, \"text\": \"Peter\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19546\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Peter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Peter\"}, {\"begin\": 1163, \"end\": 1170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gilmore_Girls\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.830257690218214e-18, \"text\": \"Gilmore\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gilmore_Girls\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gilmore_Girls\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It goes on to claim an \\\"in-depth dissection of the games\\\" was discussed on the Church's podcast, Satansplain.\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The USA Today logo is visible in the top corner of the video and text appears in the same style asgenuinereportsby themedia outlet.\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1485, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It shows footage of Paris during the 2024 Olympics, as well as of Mr Gilmore and theSatansplain pageon X (formerly Twitter).\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1506, \"end\": 1511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999973392732, \"rank\": 2.660792397313755e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1555, \"end\": 1562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gilmore_Girls\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.830257690218214e-18, \"text\": \"Gilmore\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gilmore_Girls\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gilmore_Girls\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Apostfeaturing the video on X with over 3,300 shares has the caption: \\\"So the entire Olympic 'distraction' was a Satanic circus.\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1725, \"end\": 1732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Satanism\", \"score\": 0.9999710018276303, \"rank\": 2.8999013313326036e-05, \"text\": \"Satanic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Satanism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Satanism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And now they come out with it, after gaslighting us for three weeks?\\\"\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Screenshots from the clip have beensharedmultipletimesonFacebook.\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1876, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join 73,000 newsletter subscribers who trust us to check the facts  Sign up to get weekly updates on politics, immigration, health and more.\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 2018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe to weekly email newsletters from Full Fact for updates on politics, immigration, health and more.\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our fact checks are free to read but not to produce, so you will also get occasional emails about fundraising  and other ways you can help.\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2268, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2301, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more information about how we use your data  see ourPrivacy Policy.\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2373, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the video is not a real USA Today report-the clip has not been shared on the organisation'swebsiteor any of itssocialmediachannels.\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2515, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"USA Todayconfirmedin an article that it \\\"did not report or publish the video\\\".\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2516, \"end\": 2519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999864674820648, \"rank\": 1.3532694036194321e-05, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A spokesperson for USA Today told Full Fact: \\\"The post circulating on X using the USA TODAY logo and branding is fake.\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2615, \"end\": 2624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.799124336460434e-15, \"text\": \"USA Today\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The USA TODAY Fact Checking team has identified the false post to mitigate the spread of misinformation.\\\"\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2719, \"end\": 2728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USA TODAY\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\"}, {\"begin\": 2729, \"end\": 2733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fact\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4380795511347297e-13, \"text\": \"Fact\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fact\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fact\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Church of Satan alsoreposted the video on Xwith a caption confirming Mr Gilmore had not endorsed the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2944, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2898, \"end\": 2905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gilmore_Girls\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.830257690218214e-18, \"text\": \"Gilmore\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gilmore_Girls\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gilmore_Girls\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It included a quote from him saying: \\\"I have no interest in the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 3024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having not viewed it, I could not possibly comment on, nor endorse, the opening ceremonies.\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have not been interviewed by anyone concerning this subject.\", \"from\": 3117, \"to\": 3179, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Statements posted anywhere claiming otherwise, are lies\\\".\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An administrator of the Church of Satan referred us to this post when we reached out for comment.\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Moreover, theFacebook pagefor the Satansplain podcast also said Mr Gilmore \\\"never made such comments, he was never on Satansplain, and USA Today never wrote such an article\\\".\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3404, \"end\": 3411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gilmore_Girls\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.830257690218214e-18, \"text\": \"Gilmore\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gilmore_Girls\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gilmore_Girls\"}, {\"begin\": 3472, \"end\": 3481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.799124336460434e-15, \"text\": \"USA Today\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheChurch of Satandescribesits position as a form of atheism in which the \\\"most important person (the 'God')\\\" is the individual self.\", \"from\": 3513, \"to\": 3646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Games organisers didapologiseafter asequence of the opening ceremonydepicting Greek god Dionysus came under criticism by some Christian groups, including the Catholic Church in France, as it was perceived to be a parody of Leonardo da Vinci's painting'The Last Supper'.\", \"from\": 3648, \"to\": 3929, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3738, \"end\": 3743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"score\": 0.9965392374187315, \"rank\": 0.0032956764220952567, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3748, \"end\": 3756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7153755870683603e-23, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}, {\"begin\": 3786, \"end\": 3795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9974193348379955, \"rank\": 0.0025873410895767075, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 3818, \"end\": 3833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999997890240815, \"rank\": 1.567359510506369e-07, \"text\": \"Catholic Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 3837, \"end\": 3843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5499561582030498, \"rank\": 0.8181036718866155, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3883, \"end\": 3900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7185342258506271e-13, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not the first time we have come across fake content that appears to be from credible sources, particularly media organisations-a genre of misinformation known as'imposter content'.\", \"from\": 3931, \"to\": 4119, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have previously written about another video supposedly fromUSA Todayreporting on an alleged \\\"brawl\\\" involving a Ukrainian security officer in a New York bar, as well as debunking those falsely claiming to be videos byEuronews,andthe BBCsupposedly reporting onBellingcat investigations.\", \"from\": 4120, \"to\": 4408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4235, \"end\": 4244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\", \"score\": 0.8130149667180963, \"rank\": 0.2292150677826855, \"text\": \"Ukrainian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4267, \"end\": 4275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999886299521, \"rank\": 1.1229903378877704e-08, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's important to consider whether what you are seeing is accurate before sharing online.\", \"from\": 4410, \"to\": 4499, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have published guides with tips to help you check whetherimagesandvideosshow what they claim to.\", \"from\": 4500, \"to\": 4599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This article is part of our work fact checking potentially false pictures, videos and stories on Facebook.\", \"from\": 4601, \"to\": 4707, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can read more about this-and find out how to report Facebook content-here.\", \"from\": 4708, \"to\": 4786, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the purposes of that scheme, we have rated this claim asfalsebecause this is not a real USA Today report and the Church of Satan confirmed no such comments were made.\", \"from\": 4796, \"to\": 4966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4888, \"end\": 4897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.799124336460434e-15, \"text\": \"USA Today\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Full Fact fights for good, reliable information in the media, online, and in politics.\", \"from\": 4968, \"to\": 5054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bad information ruins lives.\", \"from\": 5056, \"to\": 5084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It promotes hate, damages people's health, and hurts democracy.\", \"from\": 5085, \"to\": 5148, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You deserve better.\", \"from\": 5149, \"to\": 5168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe to weekly email newsletters from Full Fact for updates on politics, immigration, health and more.\", \"from\": 5170, \"to\": 5277, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our fact checks are free to read but not to produce, so you will also get occasional emails about fundraising  and other ways you can help.\", \"from\": 5279, \"to\": 5418, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 5419, \"to\": 5451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more information about how we use your data  see ourPrivacy Policy.\", \"from\": 5452, \"to\": 5523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Full Fact is a registered charity (no.1158683) and a non-profit company (no.06975984) limited by guarantee and registered in England and Wales.\", \"from\": 5525, \"to\": 5668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5650, \"end\": 5657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England\", \"score\": 0.832774930774718, \"rank\": 0.2003988110098001, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England\"}, {\"begin\": 5662, \"end\": 5667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Wales\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9799560303251298e-17, \"text\": \"Wales\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Wales\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 Copyright 2010-2026 Full Fact.\", \"from\": 5669, \"to\": 5701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks to Hosting UK for donating our web hosting.Privacy, terms and conditions.\", \"from\": 5702, \"to\": 5782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5720, \"end\": 5722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9997697081025069, \"rank\": 0.00023016616065740526, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Image courtesy ofLa Conciergerie.\", \"from\": 5784, \"to\": 5817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5804, \"end\": 5816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.32941521090132e-25, \"text\": \"Conciergerie\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\"}]}]}"